{"id":"guide/i18n-optional-overview","title":"Optional Internationalization practices","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"optional-internationalization-practices\" translation-result=\"on\">可選的國際化實踐<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#optional-internationalization-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Optional Internationalization practices<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#optional-internationalization-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以下可選主題可幫助你手動配置應用程式的國際化設定。可選實踐適用於高階或自訂 Angular 應用程式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following optional topics help you manually configure the internationalization settings of your application.\nThe optional practices are meant for advanced or custom Angular applications.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要準備翻譯專案，你應該對以下主題有基本的瞭解。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To prepare your project for translations, you should have a basic understanding of the following subjects.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">範本</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">Templates</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">元件</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">Components</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">命令列</a>：管理 Angular 開發週期的工具</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">command-line</a> tool for managing the Angular development cycle</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">XML</a> 用於翻譯檔案</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> used for translation files</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-optional-angular-internationalization-practices\" translation-result=\"on\">學習可選的 Angular 國際化實踐<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#learn-about-optional-angular-internationalization-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about optional Angular internationalization practices<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#learn-about-optional-angular-internationalization-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Set the runtime locale manually\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">手動設定執行時語言環境</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Set the runtime locale manually</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何為專案修改執行時語言環境</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to change the runtime locale for your project</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">手動設定執行時語言環境</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Set the runtime locale manually</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Import global variants of the locale data\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">匯入語言環境資料的全域變體</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Import global variants of the locale data</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何為語言變體匯入語言環境資料</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to import locale data for language variants</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">匯入語言環境資料的全域變體</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Import global variants of the locale data</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Manage marked text with custom IDs\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">管理帶有自訂 ID 的已標記文字</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Manage marked text with custom IDs</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何實現自訂 ID，以幫助你管理已標記文字</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to implement custom IDs to help you manage your marked text</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">管理帶有自訂 ID 的已標記文字</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Manage marked text with custom IDs</p>\n    \n  </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：10/28/2021</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\n - guide/glossary#component\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\n - guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#learn-about-optional-angular-internationalization-practices\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#optional-internationalization-practices\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#prerequisites\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#前提條件\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#可選的國際化實踐\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#學習可選的-angular-國際化實踐\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://www.w3.org/XML\n-->"}